-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pure-R port of the FlatFit baseline algorithm from the MOCCA package
(Multi-Objective Chromatographic Analysis).
Copyright 2021 Bayer AG.
Source: https://github.com/bayer-science-for-a-better-life/mocca
License: MIT (see inst/licenses/LICENSE_MIT_MOCCA.txt)

